Sentencas: Solid Oxide Fuel Cell (SOFC) stacks are one of the most critical modules in industrial SOFC energy conversion systems.
Titulo: An agile layer-resolved SOFC stack model using physics-informed neural network

Sentencas: Although the detailed multiphysics distribution has been elaborately studied with accurate 3-dimensional (3D) models, development and validation of agile stack model is yet inadequate.
Titulo: An agile layer-resolved SOFC stack model using physics-informed neural network

Sentencas: Due to slow and tedious meshing and simulation, fast prototyping of stacks remains a challenge.
Titulo: An agile layer-resolved SOFC stack model using physics-informed neural network

Sentencas: Therefore, a 30-cell stack was tested at varied temperatures and gas flowrates and a real-time transient layer-resolved stack model is established and calibrated using the measured data, which gives a Root-MeanSquare (RMS) prediction error of 2.21% for measured voltages and 1.53 degrees C for measured temperatures.
Titulo: An agile layer-resolved SOFC stack model using physics-informed neural network

Sentencas: With layer resolution, the stack model shows the voltage, average temperature, as well as fuel and air flowrates of each cell.
Titulo: An agile layer-resolved SOFC stack model using physics-informed neural network

Sentencas: Moreover, the stack model reveals the relation of voltage distribution at varied fuel flowrates with temperature distribution.
Titulo: An agile layer-resolved SOFC stack model using physics-informed neural network

Sentencas: Furthermore, the stack model is potentially applicable to stack scaling effects, or designing Balance of Plant (BoP).
Titulo: An agile layer-resolved SOFC stack model using physics-informed neural network
